title: Build a futuristic city
description: This example generates a 1024x1024 image of a futuristic cityscape at twilight.

requestBody.prompt: A Futuristic Cityscape at Twilight: A sprawling, neon-lit cityscape seen from the viewpoint of a skyscraper's rooftop, with flying cars weaving through towering buildings, all bathed in the soft glow of a setting sun.

title: Valley with Waterfall
description: Builds three 1024x1024 nature images that describes a valley with a waterfall.

requestBody.prompt: Nestled in a vibrant valley, a playful river twists like a serpentine through emerald rolling hills dotted with wildflowers. Quaint wooden bridges arch over the water, connecting paths that meander through dense, sun-dappled forests. A majestic waterfall cascades from a high cliff, its misty spray forming rainbows that dance in the sunlight.
